title: Stevie Nicks - 2007-Oct - Soundstage Sessions in Chicago, IL   A
description:
Stevie Nicks
Grainger Studio
Chicago, IL
October 2007

"Soundstage Sessions"


Source:  AXS HDTV > Pioneer PDR-555RW CD Recorder > WAV > FLAC8



01. Stand Back
02. Sorcerer
03. Piano Intro > Rhiannon
04. Crash Into Me  (Dave Matthews cover)
05. Gold Dust Woman
06. How Still My Love
07. Fall From Grace
08. Rock And Roll (Led Zeppelin)




NOTES:  Recorded back in October 2007 and a compilation of the shows released on DVD/CD in spring 2009.  Her first solo performance to be filmed since 1987.  I think it's possible there were multiple sessions in which the best versions were added to the DVD since they're out of order on the DVD from what was performed on the AXS show. 

This may have been the complete song list when taking a look at the BluRay release.
